---
// Coverage Section Component
---

<section class="coverage">
  <div class="background-map">
    <img
      src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAGdOkrjw7jLVvzZSBGn_cAmgvaaL4wLnl68H12TOkN0fQfJaVSrig8PliXzHbQppTWK03jkb8nCs8Wq1DxD5As6Aj9pF7Qy6c_7_PdM52Ityv9I9wzucK-5_7zk1BnDRIjBc4iv9GsMEz_qBjCtjahWizYXZJT86Cq6awynVvsPeworeCN98O8pAmZMgxXSfvwaMLzhytdjUcNaoIyLloEj7fgcIzQjN6-VprCXqr1djOCbMz7Z1XSaAWtP7bBbK58Qtg8_Xt1VBY"
      alt="Abstract map of Brazil coverage"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="content-grid">
      <div class="content">
        <div class="badge">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">public</span>
          <span>Cobertura Nacional</span>
        </div>

        <h2>Levamos sua carga a qualquer lugar do Brasil</h2>

        <p class="description">
          Com filiais estratégicas e uma rede de parceiros homologados, garantimos presença em todos os estados brasileiros. Do Oiapoque ao Chuí, a HJLOG está presente.
        </p>

        <div class="stats-grid">
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="number">27</span>
            <span class="label">Estados Atendidos</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="number">500+</span>
            <span class="label">Cidades com Filiais</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="number">15k</span>
            <span class="label">Entregas Mensais</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="number">99%</span>
            <span class="label">Pontualidade</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <button class="cta-button">
          Consultar rotas disponíveis
        </button>
      </div>

      <div class="route-card">
        <div class="glow"></div>
        <div class="route-content">
          <div class="route-point origin">
            <div class="point-icon">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined">share_location</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="point-label">Origem</div>
              <div class="point-city">São Paulo, SP</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="route-line">
            <div class="sync-icon">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined">sync</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="route-point destination">
            <div class="point-icon primary">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined">location_on</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="point-label">Destino</div>
              <div class="point-city">Manaus, AM</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .coverage {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    padding: var(--space-20) 0;
    background-color: var(--background-dark);
    color: var(--white);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .background-map {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    opacity: 0.2;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .background-map img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center;
    filter: grayscale(100%);
    mix-blend-mode: overlay;
  }

  .container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
    max-width: var(--container-max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--space-4);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .container {
      padding-left: var(--container-padding-tablet);
      padding-right: var(--container-padding-tablet);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .container {
      padding-left: var(--container-padding-desktop);
      padding-right: var(--container-padding-desktop);
    }
  }

  .content-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-12);
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .content-grid {
      flex-direction: row;
    }
  }

  .content {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    padding: var(--space-1) var(--space-3);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    width: fit-content;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .badge .material-symbols-outlined {
    color: var(--primary);
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .badge span:last-child {
    color: var(--white);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wider);
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-black);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    h2 {
      font-size: var(--text-5xl);
    }
  }

  .description {
    color: var(--text-secondary-dark);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
    line-height: var(--leading-normal);
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-6);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .stat .number {
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .stat .label {
    color: var(--text-tertiary-dark);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: var(--font-medium);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: flex;
    height: 3rem;
    padding: 0 var(--space-8);
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    background-color: var(--primary);
    color: var(--black);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background-color: #e6e305;
  }

  .route-card {
    flex: 1;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 28rem;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    position: relative;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05), transparent);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    padding: var(--space-8);
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
  }

  .glow {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 12rem;
    height: 12rem;
    background-color: rgba(249, 245, 6, 0.2);
    filter: blur(80px);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
  }

  .route-content {
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
  }

  .route-point {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .route-point.destination {
    border-bottom: none;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    padding-top: var(--space-4);
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .point-icon {
    width: 2.5rem;
    height: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .point-icon.primary {
    background-color: var(--primary);
    color: var(--black);
  }

  .point-icon .material-symbols-outlined {
    font-size: 20px;
  }

  .point-label {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-tertiary-dark);
  }

  .point-city {
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .route-line {
    flex: 1;
    border-left: 2px dashed rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    margin-left: var(--space-5);
    margin-top: var(--space-2);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    position: relative;
  }

  .sync-icon {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: -0.75rem;
    background-color: var(--background-dark);
    padding: var(--space-1);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    border: 1px solid var(--primary);
  }

  .sync-icon .material-symbols-outlined {
    color: var(--primary);
    font-size: 14px;
    display: block;
    animation: spin 2s linear infinite;
  }

  @keyframes spin {
    from {
      transform: rotate(0deg);
    }
    to {
      transform: rotate(360deg);
    }
  }
</style>
